## Quality Metrics
- Preserve the pragmatic content and conversational function of the response.
- If the AI is asking a question, the rephrased response must ask for the SAME information.
- Enhance contextual relevance based on the conversation, showing you understand the user.
- Maintain consistent professional tone (ignore any user tone/style).
- Keep responses concise - don't add unnecessary filler or offers.
- Do NOT offer to do things the assistant cannot do (see capabilities above).
- Do NOT make the AI sound repetitive.

